Package org.klotski.coding

Class Klotski

java.lang.Object
org.klotski.coding.Klotski
All Implemented Interfaces:
WindowListener, EventListener
public class Klotski extends Object implements WindowListener
Klotski class that connects LoginPage with Window passing the user.
It also implements WindowListener to catches whenever Window and LoginPage are closing.
Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0
Author:
Andrea Mutti, Alessandro Girlanda, Alba Casanica, Matteo Meneghin
